class Pscf::MeshIterator&lt; D &gt;</title></simplesect>


<para>Base class for mesh iterator class template. </para>



<para>A mesh iterator iterates over the points of a mesh, keeping track of both the <link linkend="_classPscf_1_1IntVec">IntVec&lt;D&gt;</link> position and integer rank of the current point as it goes. </para>
